java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants, GraphFrameInterface
public class DataGraph
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements GraphFrameInterface

This class constructs a frame and provides the context with which to interact with the Graph object. The Graph object itself is contained with the GraphCanvas object
